1
00:00:43,600 --> 00:00:44,439
Wait a moment.

2
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:50,799
Ruling.

3
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:53,039
What are you doing?

4
00:00:55,240 --> 00:00:57,039
Even if Lao Jiugui made mistakes,

5
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:59,119
he shouldn't die as a starving ghost.

6
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:00,960
Folks, am I right?

7
00:01:01,240 --> 00:01:02,119
Yes, that's right.

8
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:03,719
Let him eat his fill.

9
00:01:04,560 --> 00:01:05,640
Alright, alright.

10
00:01:06,680 --> 00:01:07,480
Go on, hurry.

11
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:18,319
Who'd have thought,

12
00:01:19,760 --> 00:01:22,280
we'd meet here,

13
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:24,239
and part here too.

14
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,560
Come on, come on.

15
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,400
Give me a sip of wine.

16
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,159
Pour me another cup.

17
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,359
In a while,

18
00:01:34,239 --> 00:01:36,120
when it's time for the final cut,

19
00:01:37,280 --> 00:01:38,200
don't you try to stop them.

20
00:01:39,439 --> 00:01:41,400
I'm afraid the flagpole has fallen.

21
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,680
This time, no one can save you.

22
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:45,760
One more sip.

23
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,680
Folks!

24
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,959
Lao Jiugui, all these years,

25
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,599
has never wronged any of us.

26
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:55,840
He's helped those in need.

27
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,120
Medicine, free of charge.

28
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,519
Treatment, free of charge.

29
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,920
Handling funerals, free of charge.

30
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,879
Today, Lao Jiugui's in trouble,

31
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:07,120
why has everyone gone mute?

32
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:08,520
That's right!

33
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,400
When my dad passed three years ago,

34
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,319
Lao Jiugui gave us the coffin.

35
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:15,240
He also cured my mom's illness,

36
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,360
without taking a single cent.

37
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,599
And the Vengeful Spirit's Claim,

38
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:20,120
Lao Jiugui handled that too.

39
00:02:20,319 --> 00:02:21,360
Free Lao Jiugui!

40
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:27,960
Free Lao Jiugui!

41
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:30,280
What do you think you're doing?

42
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:33,479
Free Lao Jiugui!

43
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:35,960
Silence!

44
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,360
You Rabble dare to revolt?

45
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,560
And you!

46
00:02:40,159 --> 00:02:42,080
What kind of useless Police Chief are you?

47
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,319
Guards!

48
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,479
Are you trying to start a rebellion?

49
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:56,439
Master!

50
00:02:56,439 --> 00:02:56,879
Dongsheng.

51
00:02:58,840 --> 00:02:59,960
Do you have a death wish?

52
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,479
No, it's a misunderstanding.

53
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,439
What right have you to kill my Master?

54
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,560
A mis...

55
00:03:02,560 --> 00:03:03,319
A misunderstanding.

56
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:07,120
Brigade Commander.

57
00:03:11,759 --> 00:03:12,120
You...

58
00:03:12,120 --> 00:03:13,280
Are you Lao Jiugui?

59
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,159
And you are?

60
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,560
Me?

61
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:19,520
Ten years ago,

62
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,719
we both served under Marshal Sun.

63
00:03:21,960 --> 00:03:24,560
That night, you summoned the Ghost Soldiers and fled.

64
00:03:24,879 --> 00:03:26,000
Li Chuanzhong?

65
00:03:26,919 --> 00:03:27,800
It's me.

66
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,520
Untie him at once!

67
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:32,879
Who did this?

68
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:35,960
Brigade Commander, here's what happened.

69
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,039
After investigation,

70
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,080
Lao Jiugui...

71
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,400
he's been colluding with the Communists.

72
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,560
A year ago, those two Communist bandits at Clear Wind Stronghold,

73
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:42,400
he's the one who let them escape.

74
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,360
Bullshit!

75
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,039
Those two Communist bandits,

76
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:50,599
I shot them dead long ago.

77
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:53,800
Don't be angry.

78
00:03:54,039 --> 00:03:55,120
They don't know.

79
00:03:55,400 --> 00:03:55,840
Chuanzhong.

80
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:56,599
They don't know.

81
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:57,759
Brigade Commander.

82
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:59,639
We really don't know what's going on.

83
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:01,719
No idea.

84
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:02,759
I really have no clue.

85
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:05,919
No clue, yet you tied him up?

86
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:06,599
Right!

87
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,560
Why did you tie me up?

88
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,199
I didn't tie you up.

89
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:09,759
It was...

90
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:11,000
You!

91
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,599
Enough fighting.

92
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,319
Listen up.

93
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,360
I've no time to deal with you two today.

94
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,399
We'll settle this score later.

95
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:23,279
Lao Jiugui.

96
00:04:23,519 --> 00:04:24,319
After you.

97
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,120
Where to?

98
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,680
For drinks, of course.

99
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,040
Drinks?

100
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,120
Let's go.

101
00:04:31,120 --> 00:04:31,439
Drinks sound great.

102
00:04:31,439 --> 00:04:31,920
Drinks sound great.

103
00:04:32,319 --> 00:04:32,759
Hold on, hold on.

104
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,680
You two come along too.

105
00:04:33,759 --> 00:04:34,839
No, no, no.

106
00:04:35,319 --> 00:04:35,839
We can't hold our liquor.

107
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,639
They're not worthy.

108
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,759
Let's go, let's go.

109
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:39,000
Dongsheng, hurry up.

110
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:41,000
Auntie Xiaoling.

111
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:43,240
Let's go together.

112
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,720
I won't be joining.

113
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:48,120
I'll bring some back for your Master tonight.

114
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,920
Don't worry.

115
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,560
Well, well.

116
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,040
After all these years,

117
00:04:55,399 --> 00:04:56,480
you've done quite well.

118
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,600
Back when you served under me...

119
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,120
Sit, sit, sit.

120
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,319
Nice little mustache you've got there.

121
00:05:06,439 --> 00:05:07,480
Show some respect to my superior.

122
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,439
Dongsheng.

123
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,800
Stand at attention.

124
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,560
Well...

125
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:14,399
Was anything not to your liking?

126
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,720
Shouldn't we switch to a bigger bowl?

127
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,920
I forgot you're Lao Jiugui.

128
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,600
Bring a bigger bowl!

129
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:25,560
Come on, come on.

130
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:26,360
Let's drink.

131
00:05:28,839 --> 00:05:29,759
Lao Jiugui,

132
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:33,120
where are you living now?

133
00:05:33,839 --> 00:05:35,680
I'm staying at the Bone-Keeping Temple.

134
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,279
In the temple.

135
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:40,120
You became a monk?

136
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:42,040
You've clearly never died before.

137
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:45,000
That place is for the dead.

138
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:45,800
It's a charnel house.

139
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,319
How can you live in

140
00:05:47,319 --> 00:05:48,920
a place meant for the dead?

141
00:05:49,279 --> 00:05:49,959
That won't do.

142
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,279
Dongsheng.

143
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:51,680
Yes, sir.

144
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,399
In Yinyang Du,

145
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,839
find him a big mansion.

146
00:05:57,279 --> 00:05:58,000
I'll cover the cost.

147
00:05:58,519 --> 00:05:59,399
Me?

148
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,319
I've got this quirk.

149
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,879
I can't sleep in unfamiliar places.

150
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:06,519
If you really want to help me,

151
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:06,959
you...

152
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:07,959
how about this:

153
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,759
just give me ten Silver Dollars a month.

154
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,879
Enough for me to drink. How's that?

155
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,839
That's all you want?

156
00:06:16,759 --> 00:06:17,720
Fifty.

157
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,079
Dongsheng.

158
00:06:19,399 --> 00:06:19,839
Yes, sir.

159
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:20,959
Remember this.

160
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,319
Every month,

161
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:24,680
give Lao Jiugui fifty Silver Dollars.

162
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:25,240
Yes, sir.

163
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,680
Lao Jiugui, remember this.

164
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,040
Yinyang Du

165
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:31,639
is under my jurisdiction.

166
00:06:34,079 --> 00:06:36,240
Whenever you run into trouble,

167
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,360
come

168
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,279
straight to me.

169
00:06:39,879 --> 00:06:40,879
That's exactly what I was waiting to hear.

170
00:06:40,879 --> 00:06:42,160
I really do have a favor to ask.

171
00:06:43,199 --> 00:06:44,040
There's something

172
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,399
I need your help with.

173
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,959
What are you saying?

174
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,079
What are you saying?

175
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,839
"Help" is the wrong word.

176
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,319
Just give me the order.

177
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,240
You see,

178
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:58,639
I'm getting old.

179
00:06:59,519 --> 00:07:00,519
At the Bone-Keeping Temple,

180
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:01,759
I need someone

181
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:03,399
to help manage things.

182
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:05,519
I want to take my disciple back with me.

183
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,040
Your disciple?

184
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:08,079
Who's that?

185
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,800
Far away on the horizon,

186
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,800
yet right before your eyes.

187
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,560
Me?

188
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,480
Don't be ridiculous.

189
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,480
Look over here.

190
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:23,839
You,

191
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,879
you're a Brigade Commander.

192
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:33,519
I knew this kid was no ordinary man.

193
00:07:35,879 --> 00:07:38,560
So he's your disciple, Lao Jiugui.

194
00:07:41,399 --> 00:07:42,199
I really

195
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:45,319
treasure this kid.

196
00:07:45,839 --> 00:07:47,439
I really hate to let him go.

197
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,639
But

198
00:07:49,480 --> 00:07:51,759
since you, Lao Jiugui, have spoken,

199
00:07:52,879 --> 00:07:53,399
Dongsheng,

200
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,959
you're discharged as of today.

201
00:07:58,199 --> 00:07:59,639
Go on, go.

202
00:08:06,480 --> 00:08:07,040
Brigade Commander.

203
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,160
I'm not leaving.

204
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:09,680
Fine.

205
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:16,399
Go back.

206
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,120
Master.

207
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,720
Hey, Master.

208
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:25,480
What are you doing?

209
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:26,680
Get off me!

210
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,319
What are you doing, Master?

211
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,360
You're coming with me now.

212
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,720
I just told you to come with me.

213
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,360
What did you say?

214
00:08:32,440 --> 00:08:34,000
Don't you know what kind of man your Brigade Commander is?

215
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:36,000
I know exactly what he is.

216
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,559
That's why I can't leave, Master.

217
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,279
What are you talking about?

218
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,399
Get your head straight.

219
00:08:40,399 --> 00:08:41,679
I don't understand a word.

220
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,879
Master, I have something to tell you.

221
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,080
Stop right there!

222
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,559
This can't be said out loud.

223
00:08:53,279 --> 00:08:53,879
Master.

224
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,759
I've already made contact with Xiao Lian.

225
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:58,799
I'm her mole planted beside the Brigade Commander.

226
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,919
That was way too loud!

227
00:09:05,799 --> 00:09:07,279
I didn't hear, didn't hear.

228
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,639
I didn't hear a thing.

229
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,720
Go back, go back.

230
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,080
I'm not leaving.

231
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,879
You just ate and drank with the Brigade Commander.

232
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:19,879
I'm still starving here.

233
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,120
What did I eat?

234
00:09:21,120 --> 00:09:21,919
I only drank.

235
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,440
I saw it.

236
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:24,759
Here.

237
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:25,720
You eat it.

238
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:26,399
Eat what?

239
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,519
Master.

240
00:09:28,960 --> 00:09:29,440
It's all mud up ahead.

241
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,080
Let me carry you.

242
00:09:30,159 --> 00:09:30,720
No need, no need.

243
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:31,200
I'll carry you.

244
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:32,519
Come on!

245
00:09:40,759 --> 00:09:41,399
Brigade Commander.

246
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,720
He's the one who let the Communists go.

247
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,399
Why would you...

248
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:47,639
He only let two Communists slip away.

249
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:48,440
But...

250
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:50,080
as long as he's alive,

251
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:53,480
he can help me kill thousands of Communists.

252
00:09:54,639 --> 00:09:56,480
A mere corpse-keeper...

253
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,759
What could he possibly do?

254
00:09:58,559 --> 00:09:59,480
Sorceress.

255
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,399
There's something you don't know.

256
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,080
Back in the day,

257
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:05,519
he and I killed foreigners with the Boxers.

258
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,720
There was a Head Senior Brother back then

259
00:10:08,919 --> 00:10:11,799
who passed all his lifelong powers down to him.

260
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,799
After he received the true teachings,

261
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:16,399
he could summon wind and rain,

262
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,559
turn beans into soldiers.

263
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,480
The Boxers?

264
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:23,440
That's nothing but cheap tricks to fool people.

265
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:31,639
Rivals in the same trade, indeed.

266
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,360
Sorceress.

267
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:35,919
I saw it with my own eyes.

268
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:37,000
那日

269
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:38,960
he summoned the Five Fierce Spirit Soldiers,

270
00:10:39,720 --> 00:10:41,960
and only then did we defeat the enemy.

271
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,960
Because I recommended him and earned merit,

272
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,279
I rose to where I am today.

273
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:52,039
You mean Summoning Infernal Soldiers?

274
00:10:55,039 --> 00:10:56,360
Petty tricks.

275
00:10:57,279 --> 00:10:58,120
Brigade Commander.

276
00:10:58,519 --> 00:10:59,879
Why didn't you say so sooner?

277
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,799
You can do it too?

278
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:07,320
Assign me two hundred men to command.

279
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:08,320
Done.

280
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,679
I'll give you Dongsheng's Guard Battalion.

281
00:11:11,639 --> 00:11:12,159
The men...

282
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,879
I'll pick them myself.

283
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:14,759
Fine.

284
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:22,600
Brigade Commander.

285
00:11:23,799 --> 00:11:24,480
Remember:

286
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,480
Secrecy is the key to success.

287
00:11:26,759 --> 00:11:29,360
Only you and I should know about this.

288
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:32,200
No problem.

289
00:11:33,240 --> 00:11:33,799
Brigade Commander.

290
00:11:34,679 --> 00:11:36,919
Why didn't you tell me about this bandit suppression in advance?

291
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,559
It's not that I didn't want to.

292
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,200
The Sorceress said,

293
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,519
"Secrecy is the key to success."

294
00:11:43,200 --> 00:11:43,960
By the way, Sorceress,

295
00:11:44,759 --> 00:11:46,240
according to reliable intelligence,

296
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:48,919
the bandit leaders are a married couple.

297
00:11:49,559 --> 00:11:50,639
What's their nickname...

298
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,159
The Twin Scourges of Qingfeng.

299
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:55,879
You've truly mastered the art of secrecy, Brigade Commander.

300
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:58,799
I had no idea we were dealing with bandits.

301
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:01,399
Seems you still don't trust me.

302
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,200
No, no, not at all.

303
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:05,440
Sorceress, how could you say that?

304
00:12:07,879 --> 00:12:10,080
That bandit couple has been colluding with the Communists for a long time.

305
00:12:10,279 --> 00:12:11,440
Once we capture them,

306
00:12:11,720 --> 00:12:12,279
then...

307
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,720
we'll know exactly where the Communist bandits are.

308
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,240
Good.

309
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:19,679
Today, I'll use a sledgehammer to crack a nut.

310
00:12:35,799 --> 00:12:36,919
Open the altar!

311
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,360
By the Patriarch's decree,

312
00:12:39,639 --> 00:12:40,879
hasten to the realm of Penglai.

313
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,480
Swift as the Penglai immortals,

314
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,759
rush at once to the altar!

315
00:12:43,919 --> 00:12:45,080
Swiftly, by decree!

316
00:12:47,919 --> 00:12:48,559
Brigade Commander.

317
00:12:49,799 --> 00:12:50,720
What's going on here?

318
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:52,960
Such ignorance.

319
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,720
She's Summoning Infernal Soldiers.

320
00:12:54,879 --> 00:12:55,399
What?

321
00:12:55,799 --> 00:12:56,759
Heaven clear, earth divine.

322
00:12:56,759 --> 00:12:57,720
Soldiers and generals heed the decree.

323
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:58,960
Soldiers move by the seal,

324
00:12:58,960 --> 00:12:59,960
generals march by the order.

325
00:13:00,360 --> 00:13:01,200
By the decree of the Upper and Lower

326
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,559
Lords of the Maoshan Sect,

327
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,200
dispatch divine troops to Clear Wind Stronghold,

328
00:13:08,519 --> 00:13:10,360
to seize the Twin Scourges of Qingfeng.

329
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:12,720
Take the order and march without delay!

330
00:13:12,799 --> 00:13:14,559
Divine soldiers, heed this urgent decree!

331
00:13:16,519 --> 00:13:17,960
Eastern troops, move out!

332
00:13:22,559 --> 00:13:24,120
Southern troops, move out!

333
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,399
Look, what is that?

334
00:13:35,879 --> 00:13:36,679
I don't know.

335
00:13:37,080 --> 00:13:38,480
Quick, sound the alarm!

336
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:40,120
Alert the Bandit Chief!

337
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:45,200
Western troops, move out!

338
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,000
Northern troops, move out!

339
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,840
Central troops, move out!

340
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:58,159
Bandit Chief!

341
00:13:58,159 --> 00:13:59,200
What's happening here?

342
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,360
Bandit Chief, look!

343
00:14:06,039 --> 00:14:06,679
Sorceress.

344
00:14:07,279 --> 00:14:09,840
Why don't I hear any battle cries?

345
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:13,840
There are Celestial and Infernal Soldiers.

346
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,799
Lao Jiugui only summons Infernal Soldiers.

347
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,600
Like City God soldiers,

348
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:20,000
mountain, river, and earth deity soldiers,

349
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:21,320
Five Fierce Spirit Soldiers,

350
00:14:21,320 --> 00:14:21,879
Ghost Soldiers.

351
00:14:22,200 --> 00:14:23,960
But I summon Celestial Soldiers.

352
00:14:24,559 --> 00:14:27,120
Heavenly Soldiers and Divine Generals led by the Marshal of the Thunder Department.

353
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,840
To deal with mere bandits like these,

354
00:14:29,000 --> 00:14:30,679
do we really need swords and guns?

355
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,679
What an eye-opener today.

356
00:14:39,279 --> 00:14:40,039
Sorceress.

357
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:41,639
So when can we

358
00:14:41,759 --> 00:14:43,440
go up and clean the battlefield?

359
00:14:43,679 --> 00:14:44,600
Remember,

360
00:14:45,279 --> 00:14:47,600
wait until this incense burns out.

361
00:14:48,519 --> 00:14:49,320
Understood.

362
00:15:01,879 --> 00:15:02,919
Charge!
